&lt;p&gt;The Access Division is looking for a highly motivated and enthusiastic person to supervise the day to day running of the Call Centre and Booking Office at Southlands Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a challenging role working within an extremely busy department supervising up to 30 staff in total with the support of the Outpatients Services Booking Manager.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The role will involve supervising band 3 Waiting list clerks, including the 2 week rule team to ensure appointments are booked within waiting times inline with Government targets set . The supervision of the Band 2 Call Centre Clerks and monitoring and maintaining targets set by the trust for our incoming calls from patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
